# No gradient text (global)

- Do **not** use gradient fills for text anywhere in the project.
- Do **not** mix multiple text colors within the same sentence/headline (avoid styling different words with different `text-*` colors).
- Avoid these patterns (or anything equivalent):
  - `text-transparent`
  - `bg-clip-text`
  - `bg-gradient-to-*` on text elements

## Preferred alternatives

- Use **solid brand tones** for emphasis (e.g. `text-brand-700`, `text-brand-600`) instead of gradient text.
- If you need emphasis, prefer **weight**, **tracking**, **underline/decoration**, or **subtle background chip** behind text.
